    <item>
      <title>特朗普给习近平机会拉拢美国盟友、修复全球形象</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/trump-gives-xi-chance-to-court-us-allies-repair-global-image</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普威胁要对美国主要安全伙伴征收关税并索要领土，这给了习近平提升中国全球声誉的机会。现在的问题是他能否利用这一点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/trump-gives-xi-chance-to-court-us-allies-repair-global-image</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普出生公民权令遭第四位美国法官阻止</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/trump-birthright-citizenship-order-blocked-by-fourth-us-judge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[第四位联邦法官无限期阻止了唐纳德·特朗普总统终止所谓出生公民权的行政命令，这给特朗普政府带来了又一次法律挫折，也预示着一场艰难的宪法斗争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/trump-birthright-citizenship-order-blocked-by-fourth-us-judge</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 20:23:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普提出与俄罗斯、中国达成协议，削减国防开支一半</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/trump-floats-deal-with-russia-china-to-halve-defense-spending</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统唐纳德·特朗普提出与俄罗斯和中国领导人举行三方会谈的想法，三国将同意将国防开支削减一半。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/trump-floats-deal-with-russia-china-to-halve-defense-spending</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 20:16:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>舒尔茨指望未决选民推动选举逆转</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/scholz-counting-on-undecided-voters-to-spur-election-turnaround</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国总理奥拉夫·朔尔茨表示，他指望尚未决定的选民帮助他在下周德国大选之前缩小与民意调查中领先的保守派之间的巨大差距，并且仍然对自己能够获胜感到乐观。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/scholz-counting-on-undecided-voters-to-spur-election-turnaround</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 20:14:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>曼哈顿联邦检察官因被勒令撤销亚当斯案而辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/manhattan-us-attorney-ordered-to-drop-adams-case-resigns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[曼哈顿临时美国检察官丹妮尔·萨松（Danielle Sassoon）在接到司法部命令放弃针对纽约市长埃里克·亚当斯（Eric Adams）的腐败案件后，辞去了该市首席联邦检察官的职务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/manhattan-us-attorney-ordered-to-drop-adams-case-resigns</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 19:23:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普要求欧洲购买美国武器以保持北约强大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/trump-tells-europe-to-buy-american-weapons-to-keep-nato-strong</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情的欧洲官员透露，特朗普总统的政府已告诉英国和欧洲的盟友，希望他们购买美国武器和军事装备，以维护北约联盟。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/trump-tells-europe-to-buy-american-weapons-to-keep-nato-strong</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 19:05:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>罗伯特·肯尼迪宣誓就任特朗普卫生与公众服务部部长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/rfk-jr-confirmed-as-head-of-health-and-human-services</link>
      <description><![CDATA[小罗伯特·F·肯尼迪宣誓就任美国卫生与公众服务部部长，这位曾经的总统候选人公开质疑广泛使用的疫苗的安全性，并承诺从美国食品供应中去除人工食用色素，从此开启了卫生政策的新时代。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/rfk-jr-confirmed-as-head-of-health-and-human-services</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 16:31:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普称各国将面临互惠关税，美元下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/dollar-falls-as-trump-putin-talk-over-end-to-war-in-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员们考虑特朗普总统计划对与美国有贸易往来的国家征收互惠关税的影响，美元跌至盘中低点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/dollar-falls-as-trump-putin-talk-over-end-to-war-in-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 05:03:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的乌克兰计划意味着欧洲盟友将面临 3 万亿美元的债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2025-02-12/trump-s-new-plan-to-end-the-russia-ukraine-war-might-break-europe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[无论美国总统决定对乌克兰的目标是什么，有一点是明确的：欧洲还没有准备好承担其巨大的负担。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2025-02-12/trump-s-new-plan-to-end-the-russia-ukraine-war-might-break-europe</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 22:00:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
